flowchart TD
    A[Incoming HTTPS request] --> B[TLS termination]
    B --> C{SNI / Host valid?}
    C -- No --> X[Reject request<br/>Wrong host or certificate path]
    C -- Yes --> D{Access restrictions pass?}
    D -- No --> E[Return 403]
    D -- Yes --> F{Healthy worker available?}
    F -- No --> G[Return 502 or 503]
    F -- Yes --> H[Select worker instance]
    H --> I[Forward request to worker]
